# Project Structure Guide

The main entry point is [src/app/page.tsx](mdc:src/app/page.tsx), which uses the root layout from [src/app/layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/layout.tsx). Global styles are defined in [src/app/globals.css](mdc:src/app/globals.css).

- The main app logic and routes are in [src/app/](mdc:src/app/), following the Next.js App Router structure.
- Reusable React components are in [src/components/](mdc:src/components/).
- Utility functions and configuration (including authentication and database) are in [src/lib/](mdc:src/lib/).
- Type definitions are in [src/types/](mdc:src/types/).
- The database schema and seed scripts are in [prisma/](mdc:prisma/), with the schema defined in [prisma/schema.prisma](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma) and seed logic in [prisma/seed.ts](mdc:prisma/seed.ts).
- Static assets are in [public/](mdc:public/).
- Docker configuration is in [docker-compose.yml](mdc:docker-compose.yml).
